isolated.description: This package provides functionality to easily use isolates like automatically setting up the bidirectional communication and request-response functionality.

flutter_fox_logging.description: A widget library for the `fox_logging` package. Can be used to display the logs of an app.

fox_logging.description: Utilities for the logging package like Formatter, Sinks,... It provides a flow to make logging more structured by introducing sinks and formatters.

behaviour.description: This package adds support for behaviours. Behaviours are classes of which the instances are used as functions.
